layout print "/(ab,fn1)/(is5)/(irdata/gui/docpix/CounterWiggles.tga)"
paragraph "Rules:"
paragraph "There are two parties in CounterDiggles: the terrorists and the CounterDiggles. Depending on the map, both teams have to complete different tasks:"
paragraph "In the hostage missions, the terrorists take hostages - the CounterDiggles want to free the hostages. If they succeed, they will win... however, the terrorists will try to keep their hostages! /p You can talk to hostages and tell them to follow you or stay in one place."
paragraph "In the bomb missions, the terrorists have a bomb that needs to be placed at one of the marked positions. If the bomb explodes, the terrorists will win. However, the CounterDiggles will try to keep the terrorists from dropping the bomb, or at least try to disarm the bomb in time." 

